## When to use this pattern
This pattern should be used when you need to ask the user for numeric values such as:
{{
    onsList({
        "itemsList": [
            {
                "text": 'the quantity of objects or people (for example, bedrooms, visitors or employees)'
            },
            {
                "text": 'financial figures (for example, salaries, expenditure or turnover)'
            },
            {
                "text": 'estimated percentages (for example, the percentage of female employees)'
            },
            {
                "text": 'volumes and measurements (for example, the size of a workspace)'
            }
        ]
    })
}}

## How to use this pattern
Use the [input component](/components/input) macro and set the `type` parameter to “number” to add the correct pattern to trigger a numeric keypad on touch devices.
